---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { defaultLang } from '../i18n/ui';
---
<Layout title="About the Archive | Sinpes" description="Learn how SINPES curates and distributes free font families for designers, developers, editorial teams, websites, apps, and print projects." locale={defaultLang}>
  <main class="view-container legal-page">
    <h1>About Sinpes</h1>
    <p>Sinpes is a focused archive for free font families. The project exists to make type easier to discover, preview, test, and download for real design work across websites, apps, editorial layouts, branding, and print.</p>
    
    <h2>Our Curatorial Standards</h2>
    <p>Every family added to the archive goes through automated ingestion checks for file integrity, family grouping, usable web formats, metadata quality, and preview rendering. When an issue is found, the font stays out of the public archive until the pipeline can process it cleanly.</p>
    
    <h2>Free Fonts for Everyone</h2>
    <p>Sinpes is built around a simple idea: good typography should be easy to access. We prioritize free font families and clear presentation so designers can judge each typeface quickly before downloading it.</p>
    
    <h2>Technical Infrastructure</h2>
    <p>The distribution pipeline converts uploaded font families into optimized WOFF2 assets for fast previews while preserving downloadable source files for users who need the original formats. Metadata, screenshots, search data, and static snapshots are generated as part of the publishing workflow.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 80px 24px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; border-left: 0.5px solid var(--rule); border-right: 0.5px solid var(--rule); min-height: 60vh; }
  h1 { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; font-weight: 500; }
  h2 { font-size: 12px; margin-top: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; }
  p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--fg); max-width: 700px; }
  .last-updated { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 48px; }
</style>
